@startuml proxy_initial_sync
title Initial Synchronization When Proxy is Connected to ConfigDaemon

participant "ProxyThread" as ProxyThread
participant "ConfigProviderImpl" as CPImpl
participant "InternalConfigProvider" as ICP
participant "ARA::COM" as CD
participant "Persistency" as Persist
participant "KVS" as KVS

note over ProxyThread, CPImpl: Proxy connection established
ProxyThread -> CPImpl: SetupInternalConfigProvider(internal_config_provider)

== Step 1: Subscribe to Updates ==

CPImpl -> ICP: TrySubscribeToLastUpdatedParameterSetEvent()
ICP -> CD: Subscribe to LastUpdatedParameterSet field
CD --> ICP: Subscription confirmed
ICP --> CPImpl: Subscription successful

== Step 2: Fetch Initial Values from ConfigDaemon ==

note over CPImpl: Fetch all cached parameter sets from ConfigDaemon\nto detect content changes
' CPImpl -> CPImpl: FetchInitialParameterSetValuesFrom()

loop For each parameter set name in cache
    CPImpl -> ICP: GetParameterSet(set_name, timeout)
    ICP -> CD: mw::com GetParameterSet
    CD --> ICP: ParameterSet (JSON + qualifier)
    ICP --> CPImpl: ParameterSet with proper qualifier

    ' alt Content different from cached value
    '     note over CPImpl: ContainsSameContent() returns false
    CPImpl -> CPImpl: Add to updated_parameter_sets map
    ' else Content unchanged
    '     note over CPImpl: Skip - no update needed
    ' end
end

== Step 3: Write Updated Values to Persistent Cache ==

' CPImpl -> CPImpl: WriteInitialParameterSetValuesToPersistentCache(updated_parameter_sets)

loop For each updated ParameterSet
    CPImpl -> Persist: CacheParameterSet(param_set, sync=false)

    alt ParameterSet is kQualified
        Persist -> Persist: NeedToPersist() returns true
        Persist -> Persist: ContainsSameContent() check
        alt Content changed
            Persist -> KVS: setValue("CfgP__SetName", JSON)
            note over KVS: Deferred write (sync=false)
        else Content unchanged
            note over Persist: Skip write
        end
    else ParameterSet not kQualified
        note over Persist: Skip - only qualified sets persisted
    end
end

CPImpl -> Persist: SyncToStorage()
Persist -> KVS: syncToStorage()
note over KVS: Flush all deferred writes to physical storage

== Step 4: Start Polling Thread ==

CPImpl -> ICP: StartParameterSetUpdatePollingRoutine(max_samples, interval)
note over ICP: Polling thread started\nReady for runtime updates

CPImpl -> CPImpl: Notify internal_config_provider_cv_
note over CPImpl: Signal WaitUntilConnected() waiters

@enduml
